<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT57">
<l>oruṅkirunta nalviṉaiyun tīviṉaiyu māvāṉ</l>
<l>peruṅkuruntañ cāyttavaṉē pēcil maruṅkirunta</l>
<l>vāṉavartām tāṉavartām tārakaitā ṉeṉṉeñca</l>
<l>māṉavartā mallāta teṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one speaks [the truth], [Kṛṣṇa], who bent the big lime tree,</l>
<l>Is [both] the good karman and the bad karman that remain with [us].</l>
<l>The celestials, the Rakshasas, and the earth that are nearby</l>
<l>are Him who prospers in my heart. What is there that is not [Him]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
